label: Symbol
desc: The symbol or the reference number of the company

label: Trading Name
desc: The trading name of the company

label: Sector
desc: The sector in which the company operates

label: Date
desc: The date of the stock price

label: High
desc: The highest price of the stock at that day

label: Low
desc: The lowest price of the stock at that day

label: Change
desc: The change in price from the last day

label: Volume
desc: The volume of the trades for the day

label: Value
desc: The value of the trades for the day

label: Trades
desc: The number of trades for the day
